B040C013V028	40	13	28	And he said to them, ‘An enemy has done this!’ So the slaves said to him, ‘Then do you want us to go and gather them?’
B040C013V029	40	13	29	But he said, “No, lest when you gather the darnel you uproot the wheat together with it.
