B041C007V022	41	7	22	adulteries, acts of greed, malicious deeds, deceit, licentiousness, ˻envy˼, abusive speech, pride, foolishness.
B041C007V023	41	7	23	All these evil things come from within and defile a person.”
B041C007V024	41	7	24	And from there he set out and went to the region of Tyre. And when he entered into a house, he wanted no one to know, and yet he was not able to escape notice.
