B042C014V011	42	14	11	For everyone who exalts himself will be humbled, and the one who humbles himself will be exalted.”
B042C014V012	42	14	12	And he also said to the one who had invited him, “When you give a dinner or a banquet, do not invite your friends or your brothers or your relatives or wealthy neighbors, lest they also invite you in return, and repayment come to you.
